# ==========================================================
# Surge P2P / PCDN 深度阻断规则集 (Unified Safe Block List)
# 最后更新时间: 2026-05-26
# 建议策略: REJECT 或 REJECT-DROP
# ==========================================================

# --- [通用/暴力特征兜底] ---
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,p2p
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,pcdn
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,mcdn
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,p2p-pc
URL-REGEX,psdk
URL-REGEX,mcdn
URL-REGEX,.*live.*p2p.*
# 以下两条泛匹配规则带有轻微误伤风险，默认注释，如有强力阻断需求可自行取消注释
# URL-REGEX,.*pcdn.*
# URL-REGEX,.*mcdn.*

